      • DEFAULT_QUIET_PERIOD

        public static final int DEFAULT_QUIET_PERIOD
        We let this to be defined as a System Variable, as we need a different timeout over our testsuite. When running on a real server, this is the default we want. When running on a test suite, we need it to be 0, You should see a property on the main pom.xml.
